{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-003__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-003", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·003.1", "text_original": "皇皇者華，于彼原隰。駪駪征夫，每懷靡及。", "text_normalized": "皇皇者華，于彼原隰。駪駪征夫，每懷靡及。", "notes": "皇皇者華 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-003__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-003", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·003.2", "text_original": "我馬維駒，六轡如濡。載馳載驅，周爰咨諏。", "text_normalized": "我馬維駒，六轡如濡。載馳載驅，周爰咨諏。", "notes": "皇皇者華 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-003__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-003", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·003.3", "text_original": "我馬維騏，六轡如絲。載馳載驅，周爰咨謀。", "text_normalized": "我馬維騏，六轡如絲。載馳載驅，周爰咨謀。", "notes": "皇皇者華 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-003__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-003", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·003.4", "text_original": "我馬維駱，六轡沃若。載馳載驅，周爰咨度。", "text_normalized": "我馬維駱，六轡沃若。載馳載驅，周爰咨度。", "notes": "皇皇者華 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-003__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-003", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·003.5", "text_original": "我馬維駰，六轡既均。載馳載驅，周爰咨詢。", "text_normalized": "我馬維駰，六轡既均。載馳載驅，周爰咨詢。", "notes": "皇皇者華 Chinese stanza 5."}
